{"tid":2074668,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"左校問卷扭曲西方價值  學生驚住填：大家打晒眼色","createTime":"2020-06-22T09:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T10:47:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"605152f1052e1f94fb46c65531b75b35199283b2","tid":2074668,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:27:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200622/M6FP5PLW6IVESXVJW3UGFZ3F6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2FM6FP5PLW6IVESXVJW3UGFZ3F6Q%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2F4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=e107736a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200622%2FM6FP5PLW6IVESXVJW3UGFZ3F6Q%2F&h=4a09861c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200622/M6FP5PLW6IVESXVJW3UGFZ3F6Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n左校問卷扭曲西方價值 <br />\n學生驚住填：大家打晒眼色<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本報獲悉最少兩間左校派發內地機構撰寫的「愛國問卷」，學生須回答對反修例事件的態度、對「中華民族偉大復興」及一國兩制的「樂觀程度」等，惹政治審查之嫌。有立法會議員質疑題目以狹隘眼光看待西方思想，用字奇怪，研究價值甚低。有學校確認該問卷的擬卷機構為一所貴州大學。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：不信任教局 學生憂評估變清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KY7VZNSNYHQB7A5NOJS3DVMCRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKY7VZNSNYHQB7A5NOJS3DVMCRY.jpg&h=64da10cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘福建中學一向重視學生的國民教育。<br />\n<br />\n該份問卷題為《西方意識形態對港澳青少年價值觀影響》，觀塘福建中學學生組織「福中本土」......................................................政治帶入校園。據悉，創知中學亦有向學生派發同一份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表明為政府等機構供意見<br />\n<br />\n該份問卷共有30題，大多與政治相關，例如「您對香港出現的反修訂《逃犯條例》事件的態度」，學生亦.......................................................只可選擇「中国人」、「中國香港人」、「中國澳鎁（門）人」及「其他」，沒有「香港人」選項。<br />\n<br />\n問卷亦查問學生對西方文化及價值觀的取態，包括「您對西方民主國家宣導的民主、自由、平等、人權等.................................................。福建中學學生阿飯（化名）指「收到時都冇意外，教育界𠵱家咁多打壓，同學填嘅時候都打晒眼色。」<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源質疑問卷設題帶偏見，「似乎係將西方思想定義為自由...........................................《憲法》同《基本法》？」從研究角度並不理想，不值得花時間填寫。<br />\n<br />\n創知中學回覆，擬卷機構是中國貴州財經大學課題組，不記學校及學生姓名，....................................間機構的邀請參與調查，不記名方式由學生自願參加，收集資料只作研究。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4WKB3C6PDPLZQCDBOQD2GMWUNA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4WKB3C6PDPLZQCDBOQD2GMWUNA.gif&h=ea49ffd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02d156bc1e0a6fcba983a42b786e75bc4c984baa","tid":2074668,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 政治審查學生<br />\n之後清算 仆街到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74a323909d198b4ac3988cbc4032e71b5c526d7","tid":2074668,"uid":231480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"其實咩人先讀左校"},{"pid":"058314973090e9e0bd235130511841ec0469289f","tid":2074668,"uid":173179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f74a323909d198b4ac3988cbc4032e71b5c526d7","tid":2074668,"uid":231480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"其實咩人先讀左校"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"派位派到左校嘅人"},{"pid":"be3215142afa4453ea3b0f0bc1e43360b511f6f9","tid":2074668,"uid":185360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f74a323909d198b4ac3988cbc4032e71b5c526d7","tid":2074668,"uid":231480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"其實咩人先讀左校"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"除左好學校有面試招生 就都係等派位架喇"},{"pid":"adaca621aacc9e5f0b9f5bba9a066c6a5cc7c913","tid":2074668,"uid":349857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"058314973090e9e0bd235130511841ec0469289f","tid":2074668,"uid":173179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f74a323909d198b4ac3988